<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/indexStyling.css">
  <title>FetchFinder</title>
</head>
  
<body id="indexBody">
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <main>
    <section>
      <div class="container">
      <div>
        <h1>Looking for a pet to adopt?</h1>
        <p>Are you loooking for a furry friend to play with, cuddle and give all your love to? Don't hessitate to adopt one of these lovely pets.</p>
        <a href="#">Browse pets</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/static/images/homepage-dog.png" alt="Dog">
      </div>
    </div>
    </section>

      <section> 
        <div class="container">
          <h2>What pet are you looking for?</h2>
          <div class="cards">
    
            <div class="card">
              <div class="image-container">
                <img
                  src="/static/images/dog.png"
                  alt="Dog"
                  class="default-img"
                >
                <img
                  src="/static/images/dog-hover.png"
                  alt="Dog smiling"
                  class="hover-img">
              </div>
              <div class="card-title">Dogs</div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="card">
              <div class="image-container">
                <img
                  src="/static/images/cat.png"
                  alt="Cat"
                  class="default-img">
                <img
                  src="/static/images/cat-hover.png"
                  alt="Cat smiling"
                  class="hover-img">
              </div>
              <div class="card-title">Cats</div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="card">
              <div class="image-container">
                <img
                  src="/static/images/rabbit.png"
                  alt="Rodent"
                  class="default-img">
                <img
                  src="/static/images/rabbit-hover.png"
                  alt="Rodent smiling"
                  class="hover-img">
              </div>
              <div class="card-title">Rodents</div>
            </div>
    
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <div>
          <h2>Why adopt a pet?</h2>
          <p>Adopting a pet means giving an animal a second chance at a happy life. Every year, thousands of loving pets end up in shelters, waiting for someone to take them home. By choosing adoption, you're not only gaining a loyal friend—you’re also helping reduce the number of animals in shelters and supporting a more humane world. Whether you’re looking for a playful pup, a gentle cat, or a small companion, your perfect match could be waiting for you. Adopt, and make a difference.</p>
          <a href="#">Browse pets</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/static/images/pets.jpg" alt="Dog">
        </div>
      </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Recently uploaded pets</h2>
      </div>
      </section>

  </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>